{"tid":2288830,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我好想quit U","createTime":"2020-11-16T20:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T15:48:10.000Z","uid":229034,"like":101,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"49df11ae1f1b2a089febb67504adef24142d5d5e","tid":2288830,"uid":229034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:27:53.000Z","msg":"開Sem到依家就黎完Sem<br />\n每日都陷入壓力嘅陰霾入面<br />\n每日都好努力去趕deadline<br />\n但永遠都冇完結嘅一日<br />\n要做嘅野排山倒海咁等緊我<br />\n仲要讀好多自己冇天份嘅course <br />\n努力掙扎過又冇好結果<br />\n好多時間忙到唔得閒食飯<br />\n經常都要食叮叮飯同杯麵<br />\n成日都要飲energy drink捱夜做野<br />\n有時訓晏少少起身做野都好有罪惡感<br />\n長期缺乏睡眠同休息<br />\n個人好攰但又要逼自己捱落去<br />\n當趕完一個deadline夜晚想瞓個靚覺<br />\n之後發現自己唔想瞓醒起身又要面對一切<br />\n所以遲遲都唔想訓<br />\n有時真係訓著左都好經常扎想<br />\n第一時間諗自己係咪仲有野未做<br />\n諗清楚先敢攤翻落堂<br />\n我覺得自己已經完全失去私人時間<br />\n唔能夠從學業壓力入面將自己抽離翻出黎<br />\n每日都浮現quit u 嘅念頭<br />\n成個人都好崩緊<br />\n到底幾時先可以完Sem?"},{"pid":"872c475600b3a285346c1ebc092b96eb3b808e84","tid":2288830,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:30:33.000Z","msg":"咩科"},{"pid":"743461d4985ad8fd05440057db51f108b3be6402","tid":2288830,"uid":369643,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:31:18.000Z","msg":"溫緊書覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40600853c9cfa8de94ae2d4d05ab91480848700a","tid":2288830,"uid":288648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:31:20.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我冇諗過quit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3c6af7a334f64d33b966435176b7bf6cdfdcb0","tid":2288830,"uid":229034,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"872c475600b3a285346c1ebc092b96eb3b808e84","tid":2288830,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:30:33.000Z","msg":"咩科"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:31:38.000Z","msg":"Art"},{"pid":"64d268ec0743f435a6ff9fadbacc48774a454