4科fail retake差d defer 5,6個D畢業<br />\n有d師兄5年先grad（無exchange當年係3年u)到而家咪又係生活得唔錯<br />\n<br />\n望返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好彩仲有個degree揸手都搵到份工之後又搵左其他科master讀，我自問垃圾唔係特別勁嘅人<br />\n如果連張沙紙都無自問真係搞唔掂（因為我無特定目標）<br />\n而家學歷通脹得好痴線，d私人公司19文職行政/中下級政府工個個都degree holder，樓主自己諗要長遠d<br />\n<br />\n香港地出嚟做野要識炒炒賣賣/投資先儲到錢<br />\n比你搵幾皮一個月都無意思<br />\n<br />\n搵d野發展下令自己開心d啦（興趣/運動乜都好） ching"},{"pid":"a2aae9ff710ad7a15d0b38d5c6229a35b50d72fd","tid":2288830,"uid":207149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以諗吓Trans科<br />\n不過唔知易唔易"},{"pid":"923d4e2c29dafffe38e01e9e9f32aec6f350a426","tid":2288830,"uid":369382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:43:03.000Z","msg":"ART你又唔係打算讀到First Hon考政府<br />\n<br />\nSecond upper/lower/thrid又唔會令人工高啲低啲"},{"pid":"c962c467d3f48663e169e3566a7623aa7e909b6d","tid":2288830,"uid":24160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92d45808f8976516939df7301a70601f19f99ad1","tid":2288830,"uid":118502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babe55a4b8c897b3c6330c2302c3a0855b9a25e7","tid":2288830,"uid":367224,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"677f805980fcf481c543436dfbe49be7ce6c14c6","tid":2288830,"uid":219635,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T20:34:46.000Z","msg":"真，又要顧高分，又冇自己時間，攞第一又唔代表會發達<br />\n不如hea讀畢業，開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"正確態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔追gpa壓力細好多 畢業出嚟考保安算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"ACO&gt;保安"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T04:12:51.000Z","msg":"ACO = 效忠基本法, 共匪"},{"pid":"e9f1c987c374b4b6791560dd5b2c889f9d03a415","tid":2288830,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0